text:
Order 3 colored mugs with some customized personal photos, the result was really satisfactory.
Colors options for the mugs weren't much to choose from, but both blue and lime green were super nice when I received them.
The only thing that wasn't very helpful, was the fact that I couldn't find any option where I could see a 360 degree preview for the mugs. It was only a flat preview that didn't help much.
